[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/68/346809.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1289431","time":"2017-11-13 14:01","userId":"windrises","userName":"windrises","userSign":"(一个纠结的面瘫伪宅)","message":"没搞过noip，也不是学数学的。不过假设两互素的数为a,b的话，最后应该可以化为证明Aa-Bb=1的等式(A,B为整数)，这个我觉得可以用欧拉定理解决。<br>单纯一个思路，我也没有细想过。<br>-----<br>想了想，还是不对","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/87/278708.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1289435","time":"2017-11-13 14:28","userId":"tanimodori","userName":"谷戻り","userSign":"(そして、谷から戻る。)","message":"没想到这里都能遇到搞OI的……<br>本蒟蒻退役好久了……数论题都做不出来了Orz<br>发现<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/jefflyy/p/7819858.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">题解</a>一枚，很惭愧只做了点微小的工作","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/78/317841.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1289542","time":"2017-11-13 23:27","userId":"smileandyxu","userName":"smileandyxu","userSign":"","message":"感谢题解～<br>我也没想到这里能遇到这么多OI选手…"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1289546","time":"2017-11-13 23:42","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"神tm猜..."}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/92/99210.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1289440","time":"2017-11-13 15:03","userId":"skysweetdark","userName":"aja","userSign":"(advaita)","message":"<a href=\"https://math.stackexchange.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">Click Here</a>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/11/21/112191.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1289446","time":"2017-11-13 16:36","userId":"halfelf","userName":"halfelf","userSign":"(a halfelf ronin)","message":"so called coin problem<br><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coin_problem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coin_problem</a>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/71/227195.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1289461","time":"2017-11-13 17:26","userId":"227195","userName":"thofoofintwsi","userSign":"","message":"如果说问题怎么来的话：<br>首先可以比较直接看出来一定有最大面值，<br>像二楼的说的，通过带余除法可以知道两个数a,b互素的等价条件就是存在A,B使得 Aa-Bb=1，进一步的可以要求 0<A<b,0<B<a,<br>这个时候(bB)b就大于等于最大面值，因为<br>Aa-Bb=1<br>Aa+(b-1)Bb=(bB)b+1<br>2Aa + (b-2)Bb =(bB)b +2<br>……<br>(bA)a = (bB)b +b = (bB+1)b<br>……<br>Aa + ((b-1)B+1)b = (bB+1)b +1<br>也就是(bB)b以后所有的面值都可以用面值　a,b的硬币表示<br>具体到3,7 的例子就是<br>7 - 2*3=1<br>则<br>7+2*2*3= 19   也就是１９可以用 一个７硬币和４个３硬币表示<br>2*7 + 1*2*3 = 20<br>3*7 = 21<br>……<br>7+5*3=22<br>然后就是自然想知道这个最大面值是多少了","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/78/317841.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1289538","time":"2017-11-13 23:16","userId":"smileandyxu","userName":"smileandyxu","userSign":"","message":"这一步就是证明ab-a-b以上可以拼出来？<br>我一开始也想这么类似替换地往上加，后来不知道Bb系数为负怎么搞。你这里点一下瞬间想通了，感谢～"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/23/302323.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1289469","time":"2017-11-13 18:03","userId":"brickmaycry","userName":"他人即地狱","userSign":"(无知即力量)","message":"在班谷米 你甚至可以讨论动画<br>给楼上的数学大佬们跪了，长知识<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/21/222174.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1289471","time":"2017-11-13 18:31","userId":"vivids","userName":"为了道德","userSign":"","message":"7里面包含2个3和一个1，因此只要有两个7就可凑出2了，其余靠3的倍数解决，因此两个7也就是14以上的数都可以写成3n，3n+7，3n+14的形式，因此14以下最大的就是11了","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/99/189913.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1289487","time":"2017-11-13 19:37","userId":"barcelona","userName":"巴达兽🐸","userSign":"(性格悪い)","message":"edit:<br>原来上面都有人贴解了 我瞎","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/84/278480.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1289526","time":"2017-11-13 21:51","userId":"278480","userName":"DrIsaac","userSign":"(性情恶劣，不近人情)","message":"day1的时候先想的是用扩欧证，然后完美gg<br>事后想了一下可以拿置换群证，楼主可以看下费马大定理的证明，有异曲同工之妙。<br>anyway，AFO<br>bgm38)","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/84/278480.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1289527","time":"2017-11-13 21:56","userId":"278480","userName":"DrIsaac","userSign":"(性情恶劣，不近人情)","message":"事实上这道题